---
description: Git commit rules for this project
alwaysApply: true
---

Never add "Co-authored-by: Cursor", "Made-with: Cursor", or any Cursor attribution trailer to git commits or pull requests.

When creating git commits in this repo, always use:
`git -c core.hooksPath=scripts/git-hooks commit`
Never use `--trailer`, `--no-verify`, or `core.hooksPath=NUL` unless the user explicitly asks to bypass hooks.
